m zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2528288\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2528288\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 09, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104hms1665702684501.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/hms1665702684501.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/hms1665702684501.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"hms1665702684501\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      $dberror\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"hms1665702684501___dberror_258090\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Return the error code reported by the DBMS.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"hms1665702684501__topic_d81752e1_d81753e1_d81754e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hms1665702684501__p_d81755e1_d81756e1_d81757e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$dberror</span>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hms1665702684501__topic_d53912e1_d53913e1_d53914e1_d53915e1_d53916e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d749138e66\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hms1665702684501__p_d81761e1_d81762e1_d81763e1\">Error number that was set when the DBMS or network driver encountered an error situation. The value is given by the DBMS or network to the driver, so it is DBMS- or network-specific. For more information, consult the documentation for your DBMS or network.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hms1665702684501__topic_d53917e1_d53918e1_d53919e1_d53920e1_d53921e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d749138e75\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hms1665702684501__d5916e20\">Allowed in all component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hms1665702684501__topic_d53922e1_d53923e1_d53924e1_d53925e1_d53926e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d749138e84\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hms1665702684501__p_d81773e1_d81774e1_d81775e1\">The error number returned by the DBMS is not the same as the error code returned to Uniface by the DBMS driver. Your driver can use <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$dberror</span> to return internal driver errors as well as DBMS errors.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hms1665702684501__p_d81776e1_d81777e1_d81778e1\">To retrieve the associated error message, use <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$dberrortext</span>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hms1665702684501__section_sdl_wst_zbc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d749138e103\">Example: Using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$dberror</span></h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">The following example puts the value of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$dberror</span>\n               into the message frame if an error occurs (<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$status</span> is\n               negative):</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"hms1665702684501__pre_drx_wst_zbc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">if ($status &lt; 0)\n putmess \"DBMS / Network error %%$dberror: %%$dberrortext\"\nendif</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gst1665702684426.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$error</a><p>Returns the Uniface message number for the error.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xdy1665702684579.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$dberrortext</a><p>Return the text of an error reported by the DBMS.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528288\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528288\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$dberror Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 09, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $dberror Return the error code reported by the DBMS. $dberror Return Values Error number that was set when the DBMS or network driver encountered an error situation. The value is given by the DBMS or network to the driver, so it is DBMS- or network-specific. For more information, consult the documentation for your DBMS or network. Use Allowed in all component types. Description The error number returned by the DBMS is not the same as the error code returned to Uniface by the DBMS driver. Your driver can use $dberror to return internal driver errors as well as DBMS errors. To retrieve the associated error message, use $dberrortext . Example: Using $dberror The following example puts the value of $dberror into the message frame if an error occurs ( $status is negative): if ($status < 0) putmess \"DBMS / Network error %%$dberror: %%$dberrortext\" endif Copy Related Links $error Returns the Uniface message number for the error. $dberrortext Return the text of an error reported by the DBMS. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}